if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('tbl_product_supp_rel') and o.name = 'FK_TBL_PROD_REFERENCE_BUSI_PRO')
alter table tbl_product_supp_rel
drop constraint FK_TBL_PROD_REFERENCE_BUSI_PRO
go

rel_id bigint identity,
ProID bigint null,
SupplierID int null,
purch_lev
purch_lev tinyint null,
create_time datetime not null default getdate(),
create_user_id bigint not null,
edit_time datetime not null default getdate(),
edit_user_id bigint not null,
del_flag bit not null default 1,
del_time datetime null,
del_user_id bigint null,
remark nvarchar(255) null,
constraint PK_TBL_PRODUCT_SUPP_REL primary key (rel_id)
)
go
